Load a TTE plan from disk

Source: R/tte_plan.R
tte_plan_load.Rd

Reads a `.qs2` file saved by `$save()` and reconstructs a [TTEPlan] object.

Usage

tte_plan_load(path)

Arguments

path

File path to the `.qs2` plan file.

Value

A [TTEPlan] object.

See also

[TTEPlan] for class details

Other tte_classes: TTEDesign, TTEEnrollment, TTEPlan, tte_design(), tte_enrollment(), tte_plan()
